9. For testing purposes and rapid prototyping, SQLite was chosen for its simpler management. Laravel handles the migration and translation of the database, ensuring parity between MySQL.
10. 
11. ## Bun
12. 
13. Bun has been selected as the runtime manager for this specific project because of its process economy and efficiency over Node.js. The repository is hydrated with `bun install` to install the necessary packages.
